---
title: Homemade Italian Beef Meatball & Tomato Pizza with Fresh Dough, Chilli & Parsley
description: Who needs takeaway when homemade can taste this good? This meaty pizza is an explosion of flavour, with homemade tomato sauce, juicy beef meatballs, and stringy Cheddar cheese. Add sprinkle of parsley after cooking for a burst of freshness and you’re on to a winner!
